WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.733 --> 00:00:01.866
I'm in the hospital now.

2
00:00:02.300 --> 00:00:05.033
Why are you in the hospital when I come to take care of you?

3
00:00:05.166 --> 00:00:06.266
Cut the crap

4
00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:07.433
Come quickly

5
00:00:07.700 --> 00:00:10.433
Mr. Huo, why don't you tell Miss Ji the truth?

6
00:00:10.666 --> 00:00:11.900
After all, your hand is injured.

7
00:00:11.900 --> 00:00:13.666
It was to save him from a car accident

8
00:00:13.866 --> 00:00:15.400
Later, to help him

9
00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:17.100
Smashed by a beer bottle

10
00:00:19.100 --> 00:00:19.900
talkative

11
00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:24.966
Go far brother

12
00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:27.100
I heard you hurt your hand.

13
00:00:27.166 --> 00:00:31.466
Where are you? I'll take a look. You don't have to go far, brother.

14
00:00:31.900 --> 00:00:34.000
Are you really going to be so cold to me?

15
00:00:34.300 --> 00:00:37.500
I was worth a kidney to save you

16
00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:39.133
OK, I see.

17
00:00:39.133 --> 00:00:40.700
I'll come back to you when I'm well.

18
00:00:40.700 --> 00:00:43.266
I knew that Brother Ziyuan was the best for me

19
00:00:43.366 --> 00:00:46.033
The food I cook for you is what you like

20
00:00:48.466 --> 00:00:49.633
I need some water.

